                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Example:&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://builds.apache.org/job/beam_PreCommit_Java_MavenInstall/16832&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://builds.apache.org/job/beam_PreCommit_Java_MavenInstall/16832&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

